SHAME ON YOU Coke Studio. SHAME ON YOU Shafqat Amanat & Ahmed Jahanzeb for singing the holy and sacred names of ALLAH SWT and the verses of The Holy Quran with Guitar, drums, disks and a full musical band. 

What's the difference between you and the ignorants of Makkah who used to disrespect the religion by doing the Tawaf of Kaba naked? What's next? Tilawat-e-Quran with Symphony Orchestra? 

Sahi kehte hain kay khuda ganjay ko nakhun na dey. You'll do anything to show that you are modern and westernized. Such jahils need to know that becoming modern doesn't mean disrespecting your creator or his names. There's a time and place for everything. 

And the hippocrates of Pakistan would've been out on the streets if such mockery of Islam was done in India or in West. But they sit quite, enjoy the show when one of their own does it. 

The people who flip out if they see their flag fall on the ground enjoy the dishonoring of their religion without protest. 

Don't protest. Don't be out on the streets. Just stop watching it. Stop advertising it. Stop increasing their views on YouTube, Facebook, etc.
